Package nl.codevs.strinput.examples.discord

Record Class DiscordUser

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
nl.codevs.strinput.examples.discord.DiscordUser
Record Components:
user - the underlying Discord user
channel - the channel the message was sent in. Null if not in a guild.
message - the message that the user sent
guild - the guild in which the message was sent. Null if not in a guild.
All Implemented Interfaces:
